@startuml
!theme plain

title Diagramme de sequence - Pointage presences

autonumber

actor Employe
boundary Frontend as "Application Angular"
control API as "Backend Spring Boot"
control ServicePresence as "Service Presence"
database DB as "Base de donnees"

Employe -> Frontend: Pointer arrivee
Frontend -> API: POST /presences/pointage (badge, horodatage)
API -> ServicePresence: verifierReglesPointage()
ServicePresence -> DB: Lire dernier pointage du jour
DB --> ServicePresence: Historique du jour

alt Pointage autorise
  ServicePresence -> DB: Inserer pointage arrivee
  DB --> ServicePresence: Pointage enregistre
  ServicePresence --> API: Confirmation
  API --> Frontend: 201 Created
  Frontend --> Employe: Afficher heure d'arrivee
else Pointage refuse
  ServicePresence --> API: Erreur regle metier
  API --> Frontend: 400 Bad Request
  Frontend --> Employe: Afficher motif
end

@enduml
